            |   LZ   |   LZ   |   LZ  | Lharc | LharcA | PkaZip
Fish245.LZH |  8:01  |  5:33  | 11:33 | 26:29 |    ?   |  10:31  compressing
            |   :55  |  1:38  |  1:43 |  5:12 |   2:34 |   2:53  decompressing

                 |                        |
                 |                        |
                 V                        V
   Size:      265721                    283435


              X      X      X      X      *       *      *      *
File         LZ     LZ   Lharc  LharcA  Pkazip   Zoo    Arc    Ape
